    <item>
      <title>Welcome to My Blog</title>
      <link>https://tang9ian.github.io/posts/welcome/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://tang9ian.github.io/posts/welcome/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;welcome-to-my-blog&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Welcome to My Blog!&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#welcome-to-my-blog&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hello and welcome to my personal blog! I&amp;rsquo;m excited to share my journey as a full-stack developer with you.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-youll-find-here&#34;&gt;&#xA;  What You&amp;rsquo;ll Find Here&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#what-youll-find-here&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In this blog, I&amp;rsquo;ll be sharing:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical tutorials&lt;/strong&gt; and how-to guides&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project insights&lt;/strong&gt; from my development work&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry trends&lt;/strong&gt; and new technologies&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personal experiences&lt;/strong&gt; in software development&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tips and tricks&lt;/strong&gt; I&amp;rsquo;ve learned along the way&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;my-writing-philosophy&#34;&gt;&#xA;  My Writing Philosophy&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#my-writing-philosophy&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I believe in making complex technical concepts accessible to everyone. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re a beginner just starting out or an experienced developer looking for new perspectives, I hope you&amp;rsquo;ll find something valuable here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
